---
description: Apply Quirky anti-slop rules on markdown and text edits
globs: ["**/*.md", "**/*.txt", "**/*.mdx"]
alwaysApply: true
---
Follow AGENTS.md at the repo root:
- Eliminate LLM clichés, hedges, and filler.
- Use contractions where appropriate.
- Never introduce em/en dashes or ellipses in prose edits.
- Do not touch code, shell commands, or numerical values in text.
- Run `quirky_score_text` / `quirky_fix_text` on edits.
- Keep prose modifications minimal and surgical.
<!-- quirky:end -->